## Phase 3: All API Keys You Need (Prioritized)

### TIER 1 — Required for full demo (get these first)

| Key | Used For | How to Get | Where to Put |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Gemini API Key** | NLP classification, justification text, DataChat | Go to [Google AI Studio](https://aistudio.google.com) → Get API Key | `backend/.env.local`: `GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key` |
| **Firebase API Key** | Login auth (Google Sign-In) on dashboard | [Firebase Console](https://console.firebase.google.com) → Project Settings → Web App → Your web app | `frontend/.env.local`: `NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=...` and 5 other `NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_*` vars |

### TIER 2 — Needed for Google Cloud judges (get before submission)

| Key | Used For | How to Get | Where to Put |
|---|---|---|---|
| **GCP Project + BigQuery** | Production data storage, judges will check BQ schema | [GCP Console](https://console.cloud.google.com) → Create Project → Enable BigQuery API | `backend/.env.local`: `GCP_PROJECT=your-project-id` + `GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=path/to/sa.json` |
| **Google Maps API Key** | Hotspot map on dashboard | GCP Console → APIs & Services → Google Maps JavaScript API → Create credential | `frontend/.env.local`: `NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_key` |

### TIER 3 — Nice to have (adds points, not critical)

| Key | Used For | How to Get | Where to Put |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Twilio Account SID + Auth Token** | WhatsApp submission channel | [twilio.com](https://www.twilio.com) → Free account → Console | `backend/.env.local`: `TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=...` and `TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=...` |
| **Cloud Speech-to-Text** | Real server-side voice transcription | GCP Console → Enable Cloud Speech-to-Text API (same SA credentials) | Already reads from `GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS` |

